{"tid":2114042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港自救系列】保安局發出左超過20萬張醫學監察通知書","createTime":"2020-07-18T13:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T09:38:45.000Z","uid":4931,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e8007861a02701be834c3429df9affd8410a1b","tid":2114042,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&amp;d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&amp;h=db2ec383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.rthk.hk%252Frthk%252Fch%252Fcomponent%252Fk2%252F1536645-20200708.htm%26d%3DgCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%253D%26h%3Ddb2ec383&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1d855019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&amp;d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&amp;h=db2ec383</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，今年2月至5月在各出入境管制站，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">向獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，發出超過20萬張醫學監察通知書。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜關注，自抵港人士必須接受強制檢疫14天的規例實施以來，每月有多少來自內地、澳門及台灣的人士，獲豁免遵守有關規定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">保安局書面答覆</span></span></strong>指出，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">今年2月共發出93602張醫學監察通知書、3月發出39211張、4月發出36039張，5月發出40220張。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，根據規例，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，在留港期間要進行14天醫學監察，須戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次，如有不適應向衞生署呈報。</span></span></strong>有關人士在入境時，均須通過衞生署在口岸進行的體溫監測和健康申報程序。<br />\n_________________________________________<br />\n保安局仲係<strong>書面</strong>先有公佈啊！！！<br />\n6月7月個數據黑洞仲未公佈出嚟啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我唔係要你入嚟望兩下比個like同dislike或者推下post就算數，係想請你行動！！<br />\n香港要我哋自己救！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n請大家支持推個post，P牌推唔郁個post<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">一傳十十傳百</span></span></strong><br />\n唔自救大家玩L完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果喺之前個post比左總共超過600個like or dislike嘅朋友傳開去，好快會令全民醒覺！！<br />\n<strong>星火燎原</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n_________________________________________<br />\n為自己為身邊重要嘅人<br />\n請大家支持抗疫！！<br />\n我知道呢個世界好黑暗，但係唔可以就咁放棄架！<br />\n點對得住果班為左香港未來獻出性命同安危嘅朋友！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b070c3693cae4b8cee5586e7aa7bdb8b265c1b4","tid":2114042,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b17c76bfa00491a6950d538174268a45714dee6","tid":2114042,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e78d063c53e2d2d7fc35e2f886a823eeed9f2adf","tid":2114042,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"推一次"},{"pid":"ec298617cd21a1e7f7bff7d47826147935079490","tid":2114042,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":